When it comes to the perfect smile, matte lipstick is the way to go. This lipstick has a subtle yet dramatic effect, it glides on smooth and instantly turns matte post application. To give you the ultimate pout, our Matte Touch Lipstick has a deep, opaque look that will make a serious style statement. Choose from our wide selection of hues ranging from soft and feminine to deep and mysterious.

Description

When it comes to the perfect smile, matte lipstick is the way to go. This lipstick has a subtle yet dramatic effect, it glides on smooth and instantly turns matte post application. To give you the ultimate pout, our Matte Touch Lipstick has a deep, opaque look that will make a serious style statement. Choose from our wide selection of hues ranging from soft and feminine to deep and mysterious.

Formulated in India.

MRP: Rs. 599 (Inclusive of all taxes)
Net Weight: 4.2g
Country of origin: India
Manufacturer: Colorbar Cosmetics Pvt. Ltd., At: C-1/ 1 & 2 , Radheshyam Industrial Complex, Asangaon. Thane - 421601
Imported & Marketed By: Colorbar Cosmetics Pvt. Ltd., 4 Community Centre, New Friends Colony, New Delhi-110025, India
Dimension: (W)20x(H)77x(D)20

Benefits

• Matte Touch Lipstick has a creamy texture, and a smudge-proof, highly blendable application.
• Enriched with Vitamin E, jojoba oil and shea butter to nourish and moisturize lips.
• Delivers flawless, long-lasting coverage without peeling or drying.
• Its high-pigment formula offers SPF 15 broad spectrum sun protection.
• Dermatologically tested.
Pro-tip:
Give the illusion of a perfect pucker by applying a lighter shade of lipstick at the center of your lips, on top of a darker shade to add depth and dimension to your lips.

How to use

There are two ways to apply your lipstick. Line your lips with a matching lip liner. Apply the lipstick directly by pressing the lipstick on your lips with a light even pressure. Press your lips together to even out the color. Line your lips with a matching lip liner. Use a brush to apply your lipstick, put a small amount of color onto the brush and then fill in your lips.Pro tip- Give the illusion of a perfect pucker by applying a lighter shade of lipstick at the center of your lips, on top of a darker shade to add depth and dimension to your lips.

Ingredients

Castor Oil, Ozokerite, White Beeswax, Petroleum Jelly, Lanolin Anhydrous Ip, Candelilla Wax, Carnauba Wax, Paraffin Wax, Light Liquid Paraffin, Octyl Palmitate, Synthetic Wax, Caprylic Capric Triglyceride, Phenyl Trimethicone Butylated Hydroxytoluene, Propylparaben, Tocopheryl Acetate, Isopropyl Myristate, Tri-isostearoyl Polygycerol-3dimer Dilinoleate, Argan Oil, Moringa Oil, Perfume, Pearls And Pegment
